A woman was killed and several people had to be rescued after a gas explosion that destroyed three row homes in Baltimore. Seven people were hospitalized, according to fire officials.

The cause of the blast is under investigation. https://t.co/zRWIgQ3sJW https://t.co/2vmHuc9s2L
